snippet.title: LEO - Badass Lyric | Thalapathy Vijay | Lokesh Kanagaraj | Anirudh Ravichander
snippet.description:
The Baddest Badass is here! Check out this full-blooded rager featuring the OG Badass #ThalapathyVijay, in the fiery voice of #AnirudhRavichander that is about scorch all the charts and workout playlists for the foreseeable future! Stream this fire song as many times as you can, because we just cannot seem to get enough! 


Song Title : Badass
Album / Movie : Leo
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Vishnu Edavan
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander

snippet.title: Ghost Official Trailer | Dr.Shivarajkumar, Anupam Kher, Jayaram, Prashant Narayanan | Sandesh |Srini
snippet.description:
This action packed heist thriller, directed by Srini, tells the story of one man's quest for justice. This apart, the film offers a link to the second installment of "Birbal Trilogy", the director's most awaited legal thriller. Powerhouse talents such as Dr Shivarajkumar, Anupam Kher, Jayaram, Prashanth Narayanan, Archana Jois, Satyaprakash and Dattanna are part of the film's main cast.
Arjun Janya's striking background scores and cinematographer Mahendra Simha's captivating visuals promise to take the film a notch higher.
We now welcome you to the world of #GHOST. See you in the cinemas this Dasara.(October 2023)

Mastering Studio : Beracha Studios ( Chennai )

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.title: Power Star PAWAN SINGH - Tujhe Na Dekhu Toh Chain | Akanksha Puri | Kalpana Patwari | Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
इंतजार की घड़ी हुई ख़तम! Pawan Singh और Akanksha Puri के साथ धमाल मचाएंगे "Tujhe Na Dekhu Toh Chain" के इस सुपरहिट गाने में, जिसे Pawan Singh और Kalpana Patwari ने गाया है।🔥

इस नए भोजपुरी गान का मज़ा लेते रहिये और हमारे चैनल को सब्सक्राइब करके टिप्स भोजपुरी के साथ जुड़े रहिये.
https://www.youtube.com/tipsBhojpuri

Song Credits:
Song Name: Tujhe Na Dekhu Toh Chain
Singer: Pawan Singh & Kalpana Patwari
Lyrics: Raushan Singh Vishwas
Music: Priyanshu Singh

Original Song Credits:
Lyrics: Sameer
Music: Nadeem-Shravan

Video Credit:
Featuring: Pawan Singh & Akanksha Puri
Video Director: Aslam Khan
DOP: Mai Vazeer Art
Asst Director: Nayan Maurya
Choreographer: Aslam Khan
Asst Choreographer: Naveen Thakur,Ravi Rawat, Karishma Saxena
DI & Edit: Santokh S Khera
Line Production: Manshi Pandey & Ashtbhuja Pandey
Hair & Makeup: Razzi & Team
Costume Design & Styling: Simran
BTS: Mohit Saxena
Blessings: Mata - Pita, Ajit Singh (Jokhari)
Special Thanks: Deepak Singh
Production: Abhay Pandey

For Movie & Album Please Get in Touch with:
Mr. Vijay Kashyap - +91 98100 34523 - vijayk@tips.in

Lyrics:
मुखड़ा
F- छुप-छुप के काहे तु निहारेलs
नज़री से बान हमके मारेलs
M - तोहरा से दूर होके जियल जाता नहीं
तुझे न देखु तो चैन मुझे आता नहीं
एक तेरे सिवा कोई और मुझे भाता नहीं

अंतरा 1:
M - याद में तू,ख्वाब में तु,सांस में तु,हमरा हर एहसास में तु
F - ऐसे न मीठी मीठी बोलिया से गोलिया दागल करा
बन के चकोरा हमरा पीछे पीछे बाबु जनी लागल करा
M - दिल के हाल का बा अब कहाता नहीं
तुझे न देखु तो चैन मुझे आता नहीं
एक तेरे सिवा कोई और मुझे भाता नहीं

अंतरा 2:
M - खाके कसम कहिले हम तोहरा बिना
दूर अब रौशन पवन रही ना
F - कैसे विस्वास तोहपे करी हो डर लागेला
हमरी उमर लड़िकैया हो मन भागेला
M - प्यार में केहू ऐसे तड़पाता नहीं
तुझे न देखु तो चैन मुझे आता नहीं
एक तेरे सिवा कोई और मुझे भाता नहीं

snippet.title: Aami Shei Manushta Aar Nei(আমি সেই মানুষটা আর নেই)| Dawshom Awbotaar |Anupam|Srijit|Jio Studios|SVF
snippet.description:
আমরা সবাই যে মানুষটা ছিলাম কোনও একসময়, যে মানুষটা হতে চেয়েছিলাম একদিন, ধাক্কা খেতে খেতে সেই মানুষটা কোথায় হারিয়ে যায়! সেই বদলে যাওয়া, হেরে যাওয়া মানুষদের গল্প বলে "আমি সেই মানুষটা আর নেই"। অনুপম রায়-এর কথা-সুরে ও তারই কন্ঠে সৃজিত মুখার্জির সিনেমা "দশম অবতার" - এর গান আমি সেই মানুষটা আর নেই শুনে নিন exclusively SVF এ।

We all were once that person we aspired to become someday, but as life's blows keep coming, that person gets lost along the way. The stories of those who've changed, who've been lost and transformed, are told in the song, "Aami Shei Manushta Aar Nei." Written, composed, and sung by Anupam Roy, this song is from Srijit Mukherji's most awaiting film, "Dawshom Awbotaar." Listen exclusively on SVF.

Make Reels: https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1497603651070341

snippet.title: Composing for Jawan | Inside Anirudh Ravichander’s Studio | Anupama Chopra | Film Companion
snippet.description:
Anirudh Ravichander dissects his musical journey with Anupama Chopra, with a tour of his incredible garage studio. From his debut sensation "Why This Kolaveri Di", to orchestrating scores for blockbuster films like Jawan, Jailer, Vikram & Leo - the composer takes us through his collaborations with eminent directors like Atlee, Lokesh Kanagaraj, Nelson. He also tells us about the process of creating for superstars like Rajinikanth, Kamal Haasan and Shah Rukh Khan.

#jawan #jailer #anirudh

Welcome to the Cinema Vikatan YouTube Channel, your gateway to the enchanting world of Indian cinema. In this extraordinary episode, we bring you an exclusive interview with the newly married cinema couple, Ashok Selvan and Keerthi Pandian. Prepare to be charmed as they unveil their untold love story, sharing intimate details that will warm your hearts.
 Ashok Selvan, the versatile actor, and Keerthi Pandian, the talented actress, have not only won accolades for their on-screen performances but have also won each other's hearts in a beautiful love story. In this candid interview, they take you on a journey through the pages of their romance, revealing the moments that brought them together and the deep bond that unites them.
 As they share their unknown love story, you'll witness the genuine chemistry and affection that makes them not just a beloved on-screen pair but a cherished couple in real life. From the early days of their relationship to the memorable proposal, this interview is a celebration of love in the world of cinema.
 Be sure to like, share, and subscribe to the Cinema Vikatan YouTube Channel to stay tuned for the full interview, where Ashok Selvan and Keerthi Pandian dive deeper into their journey of love, their careers, and their dreams. Join us in celebrating the magic of love and the incredible stories that unfold on and off the silver screen.

snippet.title: MC SQUARE | Mashooka - Official Music Video
snippet.description:
Watch the official music video of Mashooka by MC SQUARE.

Audio Credits : 
Lyrics and Performed by: MC SQUARE
Ragini lyrics by: Aazad Singh
Music: Hiten

Video credits : 
Directed and Edited by : INFLICT
Project head and Artist managed by: Himanshu Bhatt
DOP : Vishal Anand
Female Lead : Gungun Bakshi
Assistant Director : Sarthak Gorla
Assistant DOP : Luv Gandhi 
Production Head : Akshat Bhargava
Art Director: Karma arts
Gaffer : Lokendra Singh  
Production Accountant : CA Mayank Kumar 
Executive Producer : Anant Sharma
Camera : Java motion pictures
Lights : Inder lights 
Jimmy Jib : Manish
Casting : Amandeep Singh
Stylist : Akshita Chaudhary 
Styling Assistant : Udita Mangla
Choreographer : Nancy Dogra
Laser Designer : Manpreet Singh (Laserspacee)
Laser Assistant : Vidhyaanad
Casting: Raj Kaali
MUA : Monu
DI Colorist : Onkar Singh 
Vanity & Genset : Bobby
Spot : Pradeep and team

Production House : BLVCKHOLE MEDIA

Kadka dekhu baat hilaave haath chubaare aadi,
Neeche aake karle ne do baat chubaare aadi,
Tu bethi chubaare pe ger khaat baal sukhaane,
Me khada gaad teri ke me mere paav dukhaake,
Tu kadi taakti bhi konya tera naam pukaare,
Isi bijdi si padi, mera kaadja kaanpe,
Kaadi thar mere tade 1 seat khaali laado,
Pooche baap boldio karu geetkaari laado,
Main Nyu e kona pau meri fees bhaari laado,
Mere aage paache kaade suit 30, 40 laado,
Par tere karke re saare kaam chhod rakhe,
Dhara lath seat tade saare beri god rakhe,
Haryana ke chhore ne record tod rakhe,
Bhola bhagat me tere saami haath jod rakhe,
Teri soch me pada su mere din raat ek,
Baat aage kaise badhe chhori bin baat ke,
Me roj nyu hi haandu teri sheher ke me chhori,
Meri aangdi te bahar Din gin baat ke,
Tere ishaq me isa fasa mere chain pade din raat nahi,
Supne me dikhe ja s, sodhi ke me gaat nahi
Tu jimein saavan, kaadja yo dharti mera,
Tere taayi chhora gujjar ka narmi lera,
Ek aud bhole baba ke darshan hove,
Meri chhaat te dikhe se laado ghar bhi tera,
Meri saami aake sharam tu kariye na,
Rahve aankh laal par kadi dariye na,
Gel ghumne chalaange chhar dhaam chhori,
2 baat kadi kar par kadi ladiye na,
Khair Kabhi baat kiya kar,
Mujhe Ilzaam de, fir mujhe maaf kiya kar,
Kabhi palke jhuka, shaam ko raat kiya kar,
Tahle sapno me jab, mujhe saath kiya kar,
Mashooka ki marji chaale, aashiq ke kuch haath nahi,
Me te pagal hoya firu tu karti kade baat nahi,

#mashooka #mcsquare #hiphop #desihiphop #haryanvimusic #haryanvi #haryanatoglobe #rap #desirap #haryanvirap
Audio on Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd (C) 2023

snippet.title: #Video | पगली देखावे अगरबत्ती | #Neelkamal Singh | Pagli Dekhave Agarbatti | #Bhojpuri Song
snippet.description:
दिल थाम के बैठल रहs...#Neelkamal भईया आगए है दिलो की धड़कने बढ़ाने अपने नए गाने पगली देखावे अगरबत्ती पs🔥 

नीलकमल भईया के सभी सुपरहिट गाने - https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLmZzEd9Tg_lXgTQ6reFHNrnIS-kjme8VT

Credits:
Song name - Pagli Dekhave Agarbatti
Singer - Neelkamal Singh 
Feat - Neelkamal Singh And Raksha Gupta 
Writter - Ashutosh Tiwari 
Music - Shubham Raj (SBR)
Director & Choreographer Lakkie Vishwakarma 
DOP - Yogesh Singh 
Editor - LLV Lab ( Lavkesh Vishwakarma)
D.I Rohit Singh

Original Credits:
Original Album : Hum Aapke Hain Koun
Original Singer : Lata Mangeshkar,S.P. Balasubrahmanyam
Original Lyricist : Dev Kohli
Original Music Director : Raamlaxman

Lyrics:
लागता क दिही दीवाना हो - 2
फोटो के चूमे ले रोजाना हो  - 2

मान लेले बिया हमके पति,पगली देखावे अगरबती..
बनल चाह तिया श्रीमती,पगली देखावे अगरबती

रह तिया जागल, भइल बिया पागल,उ मानेले हमरा के देवता हो
कइल चाहे शादी,बाजा बाजवा दी,छपा लेले बिया उ नेवता हो
पूजा करे लेके धूप बती,पगली देखावे अगरबती
बनल चाह तिया श्रीमती,पगली देखावे अगरबती....

snippet.title: World’s Smallest Nerf Gun Shoots an Ant
snippet.description:
Creating the World’s smallest Nerf gun 5 times in a row. Reserve your CrunchLabs Build Box for the holidays here- https://crunchlabs.com

I started a company called CrunchLabs, where we build a toy together, and then I teach you all the juicy physics for how it works. So if you want to learn to think like an engineer and have a really fun time doing it, check out the current promotion where you get 2 FREE boxes at https://crunchlabs.com

Thanks to these folks for providing some of the music in the video: 
A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/
Ponder - @pondermusic   
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

Special thanks to my friends at BYU - Larry Howell, Brian Jensen, Spencer Magleby, Terri Bateman, Felipe Rivera, Jacob Sheffield, Grant Ogilvie, Bridget Kember, Bethany Parkinson, Aliya Bascom, James Wade, Hunter Pruett, Jared Hunter, Luke Gardner, Ivyann Running, Michael Linder, Brooklyn Peters, Jared Erickson, Austin Martel, Kyle Dahl, Julie Walker, Adam Sanders, Matt Michell and Barret Schoenrock.

Download files for compliant mechanisms that you can 3D print (including a compliant mechanism blaster): https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources
 
To learn more about the BYU Compliant Mechanisms Research Group (CMR), see https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/

Also, thanks to the very talented group of researchers from the Salk Institute, UC San Diego, and UC San Francisco: Lauren P. Takiguchi, Jocelyn G. Olvera, Amanda L. Wacker, Ryan J. Fantasia, Boyu Liu, and Pallav Kosuri, Wade Shipley of UC San Diego, and Konlin Shen, Roopal Rawani, Amy Cao, Mike Jeffs, and Victoria Johnson.

To read more about DNA Origami NanoNERF Blasters, please visit https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

To learn more about Pallav Kosuri’s research and to support him in making DNA machines that improve human health, please visit https://www.salk.edu/kosuri. To support his work, click on the ‘give’ button and note ‘Kosuri Lab’ in the comments. 

 
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Promotion starts on 1/1/2023 & ends on 12/31/23, subject to monthly entry deadlines. Open to legal residents of the 50 U.S. & D.C., 18+. 1 prize per month: each month is its own separate promotion. For the first 2-3 months, winner may be notified via phone call instead of winning game piece. If a monthly prize is unclaimed/forfeited, it will be awarded via 2nd chance drawing. See Official Rules at crunchlabs.com/sweepstakes for full details on eligibility requirements, how to enter, free method of entry, prize claim procedure, prize description and limitations. Void where prohibited.

id.description:
Lima kali berturut-turut menciptakan pistol Nerf terkecil di dunia. Pesan Build Box CrunchLabs-mu untuk menyiapkan liburanmu dari sekarang di sini - https://crunchlabs.com

Aku memulai perusahaan bernama CrunchLabs di mana kita bisa membuat mainan bersama, lalu aku mengajarkanmu semua prinsip fisika menarik dari cara kerjanya. Jadi, kalau kamu mau belajar berpikir seperti insinyur sambil bersenang-senang, sikat promo terkini untuk mendapatkan 2 kotak GRATIS di https://crunchlabs.com

Terima kasih kepada teman-teman yang telah menyediakan sebagian musik dalam video:
A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com
Ponder - @pondermusic   
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

Terima kasih kepada teman-temanku di BYU - Larry Howell, Brian Jensen, Spencer Magleby, Terri Bateman, Felipe Rivera, Jacob Sheffield, Grant Ogilvie, Bridget Kember, Bethany Parkinson, Aliya Bascom, James Wade, Hunter Pruett, Jared Hunter, Luke Gardner, Ivyann Running, Michael Linder, Brooklyn Peters, Jared Erickson, Austin Martel, Kyle Dahl, Julie Walker, Adam Sanders, Matt Michell, dan Barret Schoenrock.

Unduh file-file untuk buat cetak 3D mekanisme compliant-mu sendiri (termasuk penembak mekanisme compliant): https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources
 
Untuk mempelajari lebih lanjut tentang kelompok riset Compliant Mechanisms Research (CMR) BYU, klik https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu

Terima kasih juga kepada sekelompok periset yang sangat berbakat dari Salk Institute, UC San Diego, dan UC San Francisco: Lauren P. Takiguchi, Jocelyn G. Olvera, Amanda L. Wacker, Ryan J. Fantasia, Boyu Liu, dan Pallav Kosuri, Wade Shipley dari UC San Diego, dan Konlin Shen, Roopal Rawani, Amy Cao, Mike Jeffs, dan Victoria Johnson.

Untuk membaca lebih detail tentang Penembak NanoNERF Origami DNA, silakan kunjungi https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

Untuk mempelajari lebih lanjut tentang risetnya Pallav Kosuri dan mendukungnya menciptakan mesin DNA yang memperbaiki kesehatan manusia, silakan kunjungi https://www.salk.edu/kosuri. Untuk mendukung karyanya, klik tombol ‘give’ dan tulis ‘Kosuri Lab’ di kolom komentarnya.

ar.title: اطلاق النار على نملة من اصغر مسدس نيرف في العالم
ar.description:
🔫 صنعت مسدس نيرف أصغر بـ 10 الاف مرة من الحجم الطبيعي!

🔧 أنشأت شركة تدعى CrunchLabs حيث نبني لعبة مثيرة معًا ثم أعلمك كل الفيزياء حول طريقة عملها، لذلك إذا كنت تريد أن تتعلم كيف تفكر كمهندس وتستمتع حقًا بوقتك في القيام بذلك، تحقق من العرض الترويجي على الموقع لتحصل على صندوقين مجانيين https://crunchlabs.com

🎶 شكرًا لهؤلاء الأشخاص على تقديمهم بعض الموسيقى في الفيديو:
Ponder - https://youtube.com/@Pondermusic 
Laura Shigihara -  @supershigi  
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday 

شكر خاص لأصدقائي في جامعة "بريغهام يونغ": لاري هاول، برايان جينسن، سبنسر ماغليبي، تيري بيتمان، فيليب ريفيرا، جاكوب شفيلد، جرانت أوغليفي، بريدجيت كيمبر، بيثاني باركينسون، عليا باسكوم، جيمس ويد، هنتر برويت، جاريد هنتر، لوك غاردنر، آيفيان رنينج، مايكل ليندر، بروكلين بيترز، جاريد إريكسون، أوستن مارتل، كايل دال، جولي ووكر، آدم ساندرز، مات ميتشيل وباريت شونروك.

إذا كنتم تقومون بالطباعة ثلاثية الأبعاد فيمكنكم تحميل الملفات الخاصة بالآليات التوافقية (بما في ذلك مكبر الآلية اتوافقية) من هنا: https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources

لمعرفة المزيد عن مجموعة أبحاث الآليات التوافقية في جامعة بريغهام يونغ (BYU CMR)، قوموا بزيارة https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu

كما نشكر مجموعة الباحثين الموهوبين جدًا من معهد سولك وجامعة كاليفورنيا سان دييغو، وجامعة كاليفورنيا سان فرانسيسكو: لورين ب. تاكيجوتشي، جوسلين جي. أولفيرا، أماندا إل. واكر، ريان ج. فانتازيا، بويو ليو، وبالاف كوسوري، وويد شيبلي من جامعة كاليفورنيا سان دييغو، وكونلين شين، روبال رواني، إيمي كاو، مايك جيفس، وفيكتوريا جونسون. لورين ب. تاكيجوتشي.

للمزيد من المعلومات حول مسدسات النيرف بتقنية الحمض النووي، يرجى زيارة https://kosurilab.com/docs/Takiguchi-Rober-Kosuri-nanoNERF-manuscript

للمزيد عن أبحاث "بالاف كوسوري" ودعمه في تطوير آليات الحمض النووي لتعزيز الصحة البشرية، يرجى زيارة https://www.salk.edu/kosuri. ولدعم أعماله، اضغط على زر 'التبرع' واذكر 'مختبر بالاف كوسوري' في التعليقات

tr.title: Dünyanın En Küçük Nerf Silahını Yaptık
tr.description:
Bir Nerf silahını arka arkaya tam 5 defa küçülterek 5 defa üst üste dünya rekoru kırıyoruz! Tatil dönemi için CrunchLabs Build Box’larınızı https://crunchlabs.com sitesinden ayırtmayı unutmayın. 

"CrunchLabs" kendi kurduğum şirketin adıdır ve bu şirket sayesinde sizlerle harika oyuncaklar ve minyatür düzenekler inşa ediyor ve ardından bu düzeneklerin arkasında yatan, hayranlık uyandıran bilimsel prensipleri öğreniyoruz. Eğer siz de bir mühendis gibi düşünmek ve bunu yaparken delicesine eğlenmek istiyorsanız mevcut "2 BUILDBOX BEDAVA" kampanyamızdan yararlanmak için hemen bu bağlantıya tıklayın: https://crunchlabs.com.

Tabii ki müzikleriyle bu videoya renk katan insanlara teşekkür ederiz:

A Shell in the Pit - https://ashellinthepit.bandcamp.com/ Ponder - @pondermusic
Laura Shigihara - @supershigi 
Andrew Applepie - https://soundcloud.com/andrewapplepie 
Blue Wednesday - https://soundcloud.com/bluewednesday. 

BYU’daki muhteşem dostlarıma da teşekkür ederiz: - Larry Howell, Brian Jensen, Spencer Magleby, Terri Bateman, Felipe Rivera, Jacob Sheffield, Grant Ogilvie, Bridget Kember, Bethany Parkinson, Aliya Bascom, James Wade, Hunter Pruett, Jared Hunter, Luke Gardner, Ivyann Running, Michael Linder, Brooklyn Peters, Jared Erickson, Austin Martel, Kyle Dahl, Julie Walker, Adam Sanders, Matt Michell ve Barret Schoenrock. 

3D yazıcıdan çıkarabileceğiniz uyum mekanizması dosyalarını (uyum mekanizmasıyla yapılan Nerf silahı da dahil) indirmek için: https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/maker-resources sayfasını ziyaret edin

BYU’nun Uyum Mekanizmaları Araştırma Ekibi (Compliant Mechanisms Research Group ya da kısaca CMR) hakkında daha fazla bilgiye ulaşmak için bu bağlantıya tıklayın: https://compliantmechanisms.byu.edu/

Aynı zamanda Salk Enstitüsü’ndeki (Salk Institute, UC San Diego, ve UC San Francisco) müthiş yetenekli araştırma ekibine de teşekkür ederiz: Lauren P. Takiguchi, Jocelyn G. Olvera, Amanda L. Wacker, Ryan J. Fantasia, Boyu Liu, ve Pallav Kosuri, UC San Diego'dan Wade Shipley , and Konlin Shen, Roopal Rawani, Amy Cao, Mike Jeffs ve Victoria Johnson. Lauren P. Takiguchi. Pallav Kosuri’nin araştırmaları hakkında daha fazla şey öğrenmek ve insan sağlığını geliştirmek için üzerinde çalıştığı DNA bazlı makinalar ve araçlar konusunda ona destek olmak isterseniz bu bağlantıyı takip edin: https://www.salk.edu/kosuri. Pallav’ın çalışmalarına destek olmak için “give” (ver, bağış yap) butonuna tıklayın ve "comment" (yorum) kısmına “Kosuri Lab” yazın.

fr.description:

Donc, si vous voulez apprendre à penser comme un ingénieur et passer un moment vraiment amusant en le faisant, découvrez la promotion actuelle où vous obtenez 2 BOÎTES GRATUITES sur https://crunchlabs.com

---------------

In this episode of Figuring Out podcast, Raj Shamani talks with the multi-talented Harrdy Sandhu, renowned Indian singer and actor. Together, they explore Harrdy's inspiring journey through music, cricket, and the challenges he overcame on his path to stardom. The conversation begins with a glimpse into Harrdy's early ambitions, where he reflects on his dream of becoming a musician and his background in cricket. He shares anecdotes about cricket legends like MS Dhoni. Harrdy's journey from the cricket field to the music stage is nothing short of remarkable.

Raj delves into Harrdy's decision to transition from cricket to music, a pivotal moment in his life. He opens up about his journey, setbacks, and the relentless determination that eventually propelled him into the world of music. Raj and Harrdy touch on various aspects of the music industry, from the creative process behind building a song to the economics of music. Harrdy shares insights into how artists earn through streaming platforms, live shows, brand collaborations, and royalties. He also discusses his experiences working with other artists, like Sidhu Moose Wala, and the key factors that make a song successful.

The episode concludes with a thought-provoking discussion about the portrayal of struggle stories in Indian music. Harrdy challenges the notion that struggle is a prerequisite for success in the music industry, emphasizing the importance of talent, dedication, and a strong fan base. Join Raj Shamani and Harrdy Sandhu in this illuminating podcast episode, where they shed light on the dynamics of the music industry. Make sure you watch this episode till the end!

-------------

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3890 | 30 Sep 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3890: Mani Brothers Ki Surprise Visit
--------------------------------------------------------
Tapu reveals the surprise of Tapu Sena as Sonu gives an extraordinary performance at Ganpati Pandal. Everyone at the Gokuldham society praises Sonu's dance and wishes her luck. Everyone questions a little girl 'Bhakti' who had accompanied Sonu in her dance performance. Later, Danger bhai comes to the society and offers a gold necklace with modak made up of silver to Ganpati Bappa   Stay tuned for additional information!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3890, 30 Sep 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Raktabeej | Official Trailer | Victor Banerjee | Abir | Mimi | Anashua|Nandita| Shiboprosad| Windows
snippet.description:
Raktabeej is a taut Bengali thriller revolving around a sudden blast in a firecracker unit ahead of Durga Puja. Is there more than what meets the eye?

‘Raktabeej’ is all set to hit the big screens on 19th of October 2023.

BookMyShow Link: https://in.bookmyshow.com/kolkata/movies/raktabeej-bengali/ET00354857

উইনডোজ এবং সঞ্জয় আগরওয়াল নিবেদিত, উইনডোজ প্রযোজিত রক্তবীজ আসছে ১৯শে অক্টোবর,
বাংলা, হিন্দি, ওড়িয়া এবং অসমীয়া ভাষায়।
এবার পুজোয় পুজোর ছবি।

Credits:
Presented by Windows and Sanjay Agarwal
Produced by Windows
Directed by Nandita Roy and Shiboprosad Mukherjee
Story – Nandita Roy, Shiboprosad Mukherjee and Zinia Sen

D.O.P – Pratip Mukhopadhyay
Editor – Malay Laha

Music – Dohar, Anindya Chattopadhyay and Surajit Chatterjee
Background Score – Prabuddha Banerjee
Sound Design and Mix – Tirthankar Majumdar and Dipankar Jojo Chaki
Costume Designer – Abhisek Roy

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Desh Ka Dhoni | Episode 01| उद्देश्य
snippet.description:
With an aim to give tribute to the ace cricketer MS Dhoni, Gaurav starts his 2400+ km journey on a bicycle from Delhi to Chennai. On his way, he met with fans and collected wishes for MS Dhoni. Gaurav has no prior experience in cycling but he takes this mammoth task of riding 2400 Km. He faces a lot of hardships while riding in the peak summer months of April/May. He faces muscular cramps and dehydration and then plans to discontinue the trip creeps into his mind. Will he give up ?
#DeshKaDhoni #Epsode01 


Gaurav's Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/taneja.gaurav/
Ritu's Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/riturathee/

snippet.title: 50 വയസ്സ് കഴിഞ്ഞാലും ഒരുമുടിപോലും നരക്കില്ല  മുടി വേരുമുതൽകറുക്കും  ഇങ്ങനെ ചെയ്താൽ/Dr Manoj Johnson
snippet.description:
50 വയസ്സ് കഴിഞ്ഞാലും ഒരുമുടിപോലും നരക്കില്ല  മുടി വേരുമുതൽകറുക്കും  ഇങ്ങനെ ചെയ്താൽ/Dr Manoj Johnson /#drshimji 

Causes of premature hair graying

The exact cause of premature hair graying is not fully understood, but it is thought to be a combination of genetic and environmental factors.

Genetics is the biggest factor in premature hair graying. If your parents or grandparents went gray early, you are more likely to do the same.

Environmental factors that may contribute to premature hair graying include:

Stress: Stress can damage hair follicles and accelerate the graying process.
Smoking: Smoking can damage DNA and hair follicles, leading to premature graying.
Medical conditions: Certain medical conditions, such as thyroid disease, vitiligo, and alopecia areata, can cause premature hair graying.
Nutritional deficiencies: Deficiencies in certain vitamins and minerals, such as vitamin B12, vitamin D, and copper, can also contribute to premature hair graying.
Care and prevention of premature hair graying

There is no guaranteed way to prevent premature hair graying, but there are some things you can do to help keep your hair looking its best:

Eat a healthy diet: Make sure to eat a balanced diet that includes plenty of fruits, vegetables, and whole grains. This will help ensure that you are getting the nutrients your hair needs to stay healthy.
Reduce stress: Stress can damage hair follicles and accelerate the graying process. Find healthy ways to manage stress, such as exercise, yoga, or meditation.
Quit smoking: Smoking can damage DNA and hair follicles, leading to premature graying. Quitting smoking is one of the best things you can do for your overall health, including your hair health.
Protect your hair from the sun: The sun's ultraviolet (UV) rays can damage hair follicles and accelerate the graying process. When you are outdoors, wear a hat or scarf to protect your hair from the sun.
Use gentle hair products: Avoid using harsh hair products that can damage hair follicles. Choose gentle shampoos and conditioners, and avoid using heat styling tools too often.
If you are concerned about premature hair graying, talk to your doctor. They can help you identify any underlying medical conditions that may be contributing to the problem. They can also recommend other treatments or lifestyle changes that may help.

snippet.title: समोसा कचोरी पकौड़ी सब भूल जाएंगे जब गुथे आटे से 10 मिनट में यह टेस्टी नाश्ता बनाएंगे | Nashta Recipe
snippet.description:
#atta #nashta #breakfast #snacks 

Ingredients

 FOR CHUTNEY
 8-10 Garlic gloves
2 inch Ginger
6-7 dried red chillies
1 Tomato
Coriander stems
6-7 Black pepper corns
1 tsp Salt
1 Tbsp Bhujia

FOR BATTER

1/2 Cup atta
1 tsp Salt
1/2 tsp Red chilli falkes
1/2 sesame seeds
coriander leaves
1 cup water
 1/2 tsp turmeric powder
FOR ALOO MASALA
1/2 Cup Poha
4 Boiled Potatoes 
2 tsp Salt
1/2 Garam Masala 
1 tsp Red chilli Flakes
1 tsp oregano seasoning 
1/4 Cup Peas
1 Carrot 
1 onion 
Coriander leaves
3 green Chilies 
1/2 tsp Black pepper powder
3 Processed Cheese Cubes

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3889: Sonu Ki Surprise Performance
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide is intrigued by Sonu's extraordinary act during the Ganpati celebration, but Madhavi informs him that she has promised Sonu not to reveal anything. Jetha informs Tapu about his misbehavior because he refuses to listen to Bhide's accusations. Tapu tells Jetha that he will not do anything that will harm Bhide. Popatlal becomes concerned when he observes individuals requesting strange things from Ganesha. Popatlal is in a quandary since God is delaying his desire to marry owing to everyone's petty demands. Tapu eventually unveils the Sonu-related surprise. Stay tuned for additional information!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3889, 29 Sep 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:
OYE NEELAMMO | FULL SONG | LATEST FOLK SONG 2023 | LAVANYA | PARSHURAM NAGAM  @MANAIRMUSICMOVIES  

పాట నేపథ్యం:
*దీపావళి నోములకు వెళ్ళిరాంగా.. చీకటి అవుతుంది.

snippet.title: 75 HARD DAY CHALLENGE - @Ankitbaiyanpuria | Desi Diet & Workout | Bharti TV | LOL PODCAST EP - 3
snippet.description:
राम राम भाई सरियाने, जैसे ही सुनते हैं, तो याद आता है अंकित और अंकित का '75 हार्ड चैलेंज'. सोनीपत के एक छोटे से गांव के एक लड़के ने पूरे भारत में '75 हार्ड' को इस क़दर प्रसिद्ध कर दिया है कि अब हजारों नहीं, लाखों लोग इस चैलेंज को कर रहे हैं, और इसी बहाने हमारा देश स्वस्थ हो रहा है। आज हमने अंकित के साथ उसके गांव, दोस्तों और परिवार के साथ, साथ ही एक देसी डाइट और देसी वर्कआउट के महत्व पर भी चर्चा की... आशा करते हैं कि आपको यह एपिसोड पसंद आए।

"Ram Ram, my friends, as soon as you hear that greeting, it brings to mind Ankit and his '75 Hard Day Challenge.' A young man from a small village in Sonipat has made '75 Hard Day Challenge' so famous across India that now not just thousands, but millions of people are taking up this challenge, and as a result, our country is becoming healthier. Today, we have Ankit with us to discuss the importance of his village, friends, and family, as well as the significance of a desi diet and desi workout. We hope you enjoy this episode."

Time Stamp 

(00:00) - Precap
(00:38) - Intro
(00:49) - Episode start
(02:00) - Fitness mai kaise aaye ?
(04:42) - Thought behind 75 hard 
(06:32) - Family 
(06:45) - How do you manage your expenses? 
(07:54) - Reaction of village people
(09:02) - Badam Ragda 
(11:10) - Sapate 
(13:32) - Veg vs non - veg food & weight loss
(15:30) - 5 exercises for weight loose 
(17:44) - How much Ankit eats?
(20:00) - 150 hard day challenge after 75 hard day challenge
(22:08) - Ankit ki age & fan following
(25:29) - Mumbai kaisa laga?
(27:05) - Tips for 75 hard day challenege
(30:15) - Ghar mai kis se darr lagta hai?
(32:00) - Aage life mai kya karna hai?
(34:42) - Film ke offers aate Hain?
(36:02) - End

snippet.title: Asian Games: Nepal's Dipendra Airee Smashes 50 Off 9 Balls, Breaks Yuvraj Singh’s Record | The Quint
snippet.description:
Dipendra Singh Airee of Nepal on Wednesday achieved the fastest fifty, taking only nine balls to break Yuvraj Singh's 16-year-old record set during the 2007 T20 World Cup match against England.

In the group match of the ongoing Asian Games, Dipendra scored an unbeaten 52 off just 10 balls against Mongolia here at the Pingfeng Cricket Field. His record knock was studded with eight sixes.

Watch the LIVE coverage of 19th Asian Games Hangzhou 2022 on Sony Sports Ten 1, Sony Sports Ten 2, Sony Sports Ten 3, Sony Sports Ten 4, Sony Sports Ten 5 channels from 23rd September to 8th October 2023.

snippet.title: Kanha चिल्लाया Surbhi पर! | Uttaran | उतरन | Full Episode | Ep. 870
snippet.description:
Veer is going back after attending the function and on the way back he keeps thinking about Ichha. Kanha gets angry on Surbhi as he thinks that she has created an issue for nothing.

Kanha चिल्लाया Surbhi पर! | Uttaran | उतरन | Full Episode | Ep. 870


--------
📺 Welcome to the captivating world of 'Uttaran' on Colors TV! 🎬

🤝 Join us on this roller-coaster journey of friendship, love, and betrayal as we delve into the lives of two extraordinary friends from starkly contrasting backgrounds.

👸 Meet Tapasya, the pampered and privileged daughter of a wealthy man, and her best friend, Ichcha, who comes from a humble background as the daughter of a maid. Despite society's barriers, their unbreakable bond challenges conventions and stands the test of time.

💔 Love takes center stage when Veer, whose marriage proposal was rejected by Tapasya, finds solace in the companionship of Ichcha. But what ensues is a whirlwind of emotions as jealousy and heartbreak threaten to tear apart the inseparable duo.

💍 Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

🔄 Spanning over thousands of episodes, 'Uttaran' takes you on an emotional roller-coaster, exploring the lives of these characters, their triumphs, their struggles, and the undeniable fate that intertwines their destinies.

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 As the story unfolds, follow the lives of their children and witness how the choices made by their parents continue to shape their future, testing their bonds and unraveling new mysteries.

🔥 Brace yourself for a gripping tale of love, loyalty, and sacrifice that will keep you on the edge of your seats, episode after episode.

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3889 - Kya Sonu Banegi Tapu Ki Jeevan Saathi?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah |तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.title: Mission Raniganj: The Great Bharat Rescue | Official Trailer | Akshay Kumar | In Cinemas 6th October
snippet.description:
Get ready to witness one of the largest coal mine rescue missions, INSPIRED BY A REAL HERO, Jaswant Singh Gill! ✨

#MissionRaniganj IN CINEMAS on 6th October.

Book your tickets on BookMyShow and get ₹200 off* - https://in.bookmyshow.com/movie-voucher/BSTR/2001373 

MISSION RANIGANJ - The Great Bharat Rescue is inspired by a real-life hero, Late Jaswant Singh Gill, an engineer who led a challenging rescue mission to save trapped miners from a flooded coal mine. This edge-of-the-seat thriller highlights Gill's courage and relentless efforts, showcasing his resilience to overcome adversities. A race against time rescue mission starring Akshay Kumar and Parineeti Chopra in the lead with a talented ensemble cast - Kumund Mishra, Rajesh Sharma, Pavan Malhotra, Ravi Kishan, Dibyendu Bhattacharya and Varun Badola to name a few.
